<h1 class="name post-title entry-title" itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing"><span itemprop="name">New coronavirus treatment helps the infected get better WITHIN DAYS</span></h1>
By Daily Mail UK 
<div class="story-date">April 7, 2020</div>
<div class="entry">
<h4>&nbsp;Share This On:</h4>
<div class="swp_social_panel swp_horizontal_panel swp_flat_fresh  swp_default_full_color swp_individual_full_color swp_other_full_color scale-100  scale-" data-min-width="1100" data-float-color="#ffffff" data-float="bottom" data-float-mobile="bottom" data-transition="slide"><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_twitter" data-network="twitter"><a class="nc_tweet swp_share_link" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=New+coronavirus+treatment+helps+the+infected+get+better+WITHIN+DAYS&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stlucianewsonline.com%2Fnew-coronavirus-treatment-helps-the-infected-get-better-within-days%2F" data-link="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=New+coronavirus+treatment+helps+the+infected+get+better+WITHIN+DAYS&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stlucianewsonline.com%2Fnew-coronavirus-treatment-helps-the-infected-get-better-within-days%2F"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw swp_twitter_icon"></i><span class="swp_share">Tweet</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_pinterest" data-network="pinterest"><a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="nc_tweet swp_share_link noPop" onClick="var e=document.createElement('script');
